Start by discretizing the time into a uniformly spaced grid between "t0" and "tf". This will be assigned to variable "T". Choose a suitable step. Starting with the initial conditions, solve the system iteratively by using the update rule presented in equation 5. Carefully determine the slopes k1 through k5 at each time step, for theta and w seperately. You are given the following code in matlab just fill it in : 
